          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The process begins with a 3D foot scan in store. Consumers are able to instantly view their 3D foot measurements and immediately receive their unique foot profile data via email. Retailers who fully integrate the program can then have FitGenius recommendations appear wherever the consumer shops- whether in store, on their website or through their email blasts and social media channels. The process is easy, engaging, and fun for the shopper and allows them to get the right fit on the first try. Retailers benefit from reduced online returns, increased customer satisfaction and customer loyalty.<br/><br/></p>",
